      <title>韩国热门股票上涨 250% 后，对冲基金进一步获利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/hedge-funds-see-further-gain-in-hot-korean-stock-after-250-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国一家辣味方便面制造商的股价上涨了 250%，帮助一些对冲基金度过了去年亚洲表现最差的市场。他们押注该股将在 2025 年延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/hedge-funds-see-further-gain-in-hot-korean-stock-after-250-jump</guid>
